@@TJvDateTimePicker
<TITLEIMG TJvDateTimePicker>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.CommCtrl,JVCL.DateTime.EditsCombos,JVCL.EditsMemosAndCombos.Edits,JVCL.SelectAndChoose
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  Use this component to let the user input a date or time.
Description
  This component is derived from the VCL DateTimePicker. Its enhanced in that it offers events for
  mouse entering and leaving as well as the OnParentColorChange event which gets triggered when the
  color of the components parent changes. Further it provides a hint color property which can be used
  to set the background color of the components hint box.

